::KitKat::

She looked at Quickstrike and watched as he wobbled out of the 
chamber.  She came up beside him and put her arm under his 
shoulder. "You just take it easy boss bot.  I'll help you get to your 
quarters. Other than the head ache, how are you feeling? You going to 
die on us?"  She was hoping to get him in his vulnerable spot, his 
ego. She was smiling and hoping for a snappy come back.




--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Talon Harvilicz" <wilddance_mare@h...> 
wrote:
> Quickstrike:
> 
> 
> Quickstrike opened his eyes, hearing two female voices. He quickly 
dimed his 
> optics as his head rushed. He groaned deeply. Besides the pain in 
his head, 
> he wasn't in a very comfortable position. He leaned over, and 
nearly lost 
> his balance, despite being seated. He put his legs out to the side 
which 
> made things a little better.
> 
> "Tarnation," he mumbled while opening his eyes again. He saw 
Stingtra and 
> KitKat. He struggled to stand up and get his balance. He stepped 
out leaned 
> heavily on the side of the chamber. He held his head.
> 
> "Ah got th' worst headache and ah'm dizzy," he mumbled. "Tired 
too." he 
> added. He felt like he was going to pass out. "Ah'm gonna lie 
down." He 
> walked off into the main section of the room.
